\FF[nako_smiletyu]Nadeshiko: "Akane... Thank you for always being there. For
coming to visit me."
\F[beni_smiletyu]\FF[nako_smiletyu]\AA[1]Akane: "The person just now... was that a detective?"
\F[beni_smiletyu]\FF[nako_smiletyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Yeah... I'm a little tired, I guess..."
\F[beni_smiletyu]\FF[nako_smiletyu]\AA[1]Akane: "Can you tell me the same story...?"
\F[beni_smiletyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Eh?"

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[1]Akane: "The culprit. The story about the culprit. If they
haven't been caught yet... we need to do something."
\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "That's... none of your business, right?"

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[1]Akane: "Why not?! I can't just let someone who did such a
thing go free!"

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Even if... you find the culprit, what will you
do?"

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[1]Akane: "I'll make them pay! They'll receive their
retribution and be thrown in jail!"
\FF[nako_troubletyu]Nadeshiko: "Akane... don't you understand?"

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[1]Akane: "Understand what? Ah! You think that me, a child,
trying hard won't be of any use? That's not true! From a
different perspective than the police..."

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "You don't understand. You don't even know how I
feel... how could you possibly find the culprit?"

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_troubletyu]\AA[1]Akane: "Nadeshiko is just pretending to be strong! In
reality... you want the culprit to be caught, right?!"
\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "After all, nothing... ugh... sniffle..."
\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[1]Akane: "I'm sorry. I didn't mean to make you cry..."

\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "You did. It's terrible... Akane. You don't
understand my feelings at all!! I was happy when you came
today..."
\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[1]Akane: "Eh...?"

\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "The detective asked me... sniffle... sniffle...
so many strange questions... I hated it! That's why when
Akane came... I thought we could talk about school and
stuff..."

\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "But instead, you bring up the same topic! I hate
it...! I'm sick of it...!!"
\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[1]Akane: "That's not what I..."

\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[2]Nadeshiko: "Get out! You don't understand people's feelings
at all... You're just spinning your wheels, Akane!"
\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[nako_crytyu]\AA[1]Akane: "I am... ugh..."
